---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy | Anastasia Tulentseva"
  description="Privacy policy for anastasia.tulentsev.com"
>
  <main class="w-full max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-8">Privacy</h1>
    <div class="text-gray-600 space-y-6">
      <p>
        I use Google Analytics to see how many people visit this site and which
        parts they find interesting. This helps me keep the site fast and the
        content relevant.
      </p>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-2">
          What is collected?
        </h2>
        <p>
          Google Analytics uses cookies to collect anonymous data like your
          browser type, device, and which sections of this page you view. I have
          enabled IP Anonymization, so your full IP address is never stored or
          shared with me.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2">
          Data is processed by Google; see{" "}
          <a
            href="https://policies.google.com/privacy"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-gold hover:underline"
          >
            Google's privacy policy
          </a>
          .
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-2">
          Your control
        </h2>
        <p>
          If you'd rather not be tracked, you can decline cookies on the entry
          banner.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal mb-2">
          Contact
        </h2>
        <p>
          Questions? Email me via the Get in Touch button above.
        </p>
      </section>

      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 pt-2">Last updated: February 2026.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
